Notes on running waveshare 2.13inch e-Paper_HAT

See following websites
https://www.waveshare.com/wiki/2.13inch_e-Paper_HAT
https://www.waveshare.com/wiki/Pioneer600#Libraries_Installation_for_RPi

Installing necessary libraries
==============================
sudo apt-get install python-dev python-smbus python-serial python-imaging

Installing spidev
=================
Note this must be none using sudo
---------------------------------
sudo apt-get install python-pip
sudo pip install spidev

Configuration
=============
Enable the SPI and I2C modules using raspi-config

Check that the following two lines in the /etc/modules configuration file 
i2c-bcm2708 
i2c-dev 

Demo software
=============
https://www.waveshare.com/wiki/File:2.13inch_e-Paper_HAT-code.7z

Pin outs
==========
DC Pin22/GPIO25 
RST Pin11/GPIO17 
BUSY Pin18/GPIO24  

